<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Andreas Christensen has been sent off against Liverpool after bringing down Sadio Mane who was through on goal.</p>

<p>Jordan Henderson's long ball caught out the Chelsea defence with Christensen bundling Mane to the ground before he could knock the ball past the on-rushing Kepa Arrizabalaga.</p>

<p>Referee Paul Tierney originally gave the Blues' defender a yellow card but that was upgraded to a red after the official was advised to check the pitch-side monitor by VAR.</p>

<p>Andreas Christensen has been sent off against Liverpool after bringing down Sadio Mane</p>
